claim.claim-text:
1. A modular belt link comprising: 
a link base having at least one hinge barrel for connecting the link to adjacent links, said link base having a direction of travel; 
a side guard fixed to said link base, and defining a non-planar wall having a bottom and top joined by sides, said wall being twisted relative an axis of rotation extending through said top and bottom.

13. A belt link comprising: 
a link base having at least one hinge barrel for connecting the link to adjacent links, said link base having a direction of travel; 
a side guard fixed to said link base, and including a non-planar wall defined by a top edge and bottom edge joined by side edges, said non-planar wall including an axis of rotating extending between said top edge and said bottom edge, wherein said non-planar wall is twisted relative to said axis of rotation.
